\fs36 \cf0 Human
\fs22 \
Humans are a versatile race.  They are slightly stronger and more accurate with weapons, making them natural Archers, but they are a solid choice for other roles as well.  However, Humans lack the magical spark that brings luck, so they seldom make good Thieves.
