\fs36 \cf0 Gnome
\fs22 \
Gnomes may be short and lack strength, but they have deceptively fast hands.  They are known to be grumpy, but the touch of magic that runs through their veins makes them luckier than any other race.  You may not like them, but they make excellent Thieves, and parties without a Thief on their side will regret it.
