\fs36 \cf0 Pixie
\fs22 \
The Pixie is a tiny winged creature from the ancient world, but a few are still known to exist.  Their obvious lack of strength is more than made up for by their other significant advantages, including speed to keep their fragile bodies away from the melee.  They are the most intelligent race, making excellent Sorcerers and Clerics.  Pixies speak their own language, and sing so well they even make good Bards.
